Walking into 2023 with 0 regrets
2022 was nothing but a blessing! I took a 2 month mental health break to pray, and set intentions going into the new year and what’s about to happen! It’s not easy to believe in yourself when this entertainment industry is filled with fake smiles and broken promises, but still, I RISE! 2023 is going to be one of the BIGGEST years in my career and I CANT WAIT to show the world what hard work, tears, passion, sacrifice, happiness, rejoice, and belief (in myself) looks like. They say if you don’t get a seat at the table to build your own, and this table took 15 years of building 💕🙏🏾💕
See y’all in 2023 💕
